

### 1. 회원가입 (POST /users/signup)
POST http://localhost:3000/users/signup
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "test@example.com",
  "nickname": "테스트유저",
  "password": "password123"
}

### 2. 로그인 (POST /users/login)
POST http://localhost:3000/users/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "test@example.com",
  "password": "password123"
}

### 3. 토큰 갱신 (POST /users/refresh)
# 위 로그인 응답에서 받은 refreshToken을 사용하세요
POST http://localhost:3000/users/refresh
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "refreshToken": "your-refresh-token-here"
}

### 4. 내 정보 조회 (GET /users/me)
# 로그인 후 받은 accessToken을 Authorization 헤더에 넣으세요
GET http://localhost:3000/users/me
Authorization: Bearer your-access-token-here
Accept: application/json

### 5. 내 정보 수정 (PATCH /users/me)
PATCH http://localhost:3000/users/me
Authorization: Bearer your-access-token-here
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "nickname": "수정된닉네임",
  "image": "https://example.com/image.jpg"
}

### 6. 비밀번호 변경 (PATCH /users/me/password)
PATCH http://localhost:3000/users/me/password
Authorization: Bearer your-access-token-here
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "currentPassword": "password123",
  "newPassword": "newpassword456"
}

### 7. 내가 등록한 상품 목록 조회 (GET /users/me/products)
GET http://localhost:3000/users/me/products
Authorization: Bearer your-access-token-here
Accept: application/json


